trends: There have been no other sightings in Preston

divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside at around 7:30 playing basketball by myself and I started to hear like vibrating and pulsating sounds I saw a big flash to the left of me I looked over and I could see a sphere flying in a snakelike fashion and then it stopped and hovered for about five minutes and then the pulsating got louder and it started to give me a headache so I turned to go and get someone and it just disappeared but it left behind a cloud with the same exact shape as what I saw
